42:39.792 --> 42:41.625
[door opens, closes]

42:48.166 --> 42:51.166
♪ You're here ♪

42:51.166 --> 42:54.166
♪ And so am I ♪

42:54.166 --> 42:59.291
♪♪♪

43:03.041 --> 43:05.000
You all right?

