I just...

44:10.417 --> 44:12.583
That's not us anymore.

44:14.750 --> 44:16.917
Abs.

44:16.917 --> 44:18.792
I'm not that anymore.

44:27.291 --> 44:30.667
I know.

44:30.667 --> 44:31.166
♪ And I only have ♪

